y one person views Noah Lyles will change this week, in Paris.\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 560, \"end\": 570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 597, \"end\": 602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.884761056043172e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His mother understands this, but she knows him.\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 651, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She knows that many will get things right about her son and others will get things so-so-so-so wrong.\", \"from\": 652, \"to\": 753, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Keisha knows that some people will see or hear her ever-more accessible son and think: \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cNot for me.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d But she does not spend even a millisecond on the notion that her son just wants attention.\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 950, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 755, \"end\": 761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keisha_Buchanan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keisha\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keisha_Buchanan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keisha_Buchanan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She waves that nonsense away.\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 980, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She always encouraged Noah and his two siblings to be whatever they wanted.\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 1057, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1004, \"end\": 1008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"score\": 0.9996239095009498, \"rank\": 0.00037022851452198075, \"text\": \"Noah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", 