"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"2: At the U.S. Track and Field trials in June, Lyles pulled out a series of Yu-Gi-Oh!\", \"from\": 2296, \"to\": 2381, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2343, \"end\": 2348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.7652086834710999, \"rank\": 0.30682580981056595, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"cards before races.\", \"from\": 2382, \"to\": 2401, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cA lot of people were scrambling like me to figure out the meaning,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Keisha says.\", \"from\": 2402, \"to\": 2487, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2475, \"end\": 2481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keisha_Buchanan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keisha\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keisha_Buchanan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keisha_Buchanan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t know the meaning of those!\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2527, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It means he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s living his best life.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Then, she says, after the 200-meter finals, Lyles walked into the stadium with a toy water gun.\", \"from\": 2528, \"to\": 2664, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2613, \"end\": 2618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.7652086834710999, \"rank\": 0.30682580981056595, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Keisha and Noah\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s father, Kevin Lyles\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094both former college track athletes\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094were confused.\\u00c2  Kevin asked, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI thought we were trying to make that Olympic team.\", \"from\": 2665, \"to\": 2828, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2665, \"end\": 2671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keisha_Buchanan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keisha\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keisha_Buchanan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keisha_Buchanan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Are we out here playing with toys?\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Over the past three years, everything changed for Noah Lyles, his immediate family and everyone else in his inner orbit.\", \"from\": 2829, \"to\": 2988, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2918, \"end\": 2928, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before the Tokyo Games in 2021, Lyles dealt with depression and anxiety, speaking openly about having been bullied, severe bouts of childhood asthma and twin diagnoses of Attention Deficit Disorder and Dyslexia.\", \"from\": 2989, \"to\": 3200, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3021, \"end\": 3026, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.7652086834710999, \"rank\": 0.30682580981056595, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 3160, \"end\": 3186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Attention_deficit_hyperactivity_disorder\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Attention Deficit Disorder\", \"types\": [\"Q12136\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Attention_deficit_hyperactivity_disorder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Attention_deficit_hyperactivity_disorder\"}, {\