u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s his journey from one Olympics to another.\", \"from\": 3521, \"to\": 3574, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s always been his own person.\", \"from\": 3575, \"to\": 3609, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When we went to Tokyo, there was a lot more pressure, a lot more weight.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Hence the focus of these past three years.\", \"from\": 3610, \"to\": 3729, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3626, \"end\": 3631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999724683245574, \"rank\": 2.7494456151700106e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As much as there were tweaks to his form or fitness, Lyles also lasered in on understanding of self and his mental health.\", \"from\": 3730, \"to\": 3852, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3783, \"end\": 3788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.7652086834710999, \"rank\": 0.30682580981056595, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Improving those, he discovered, made him faster.\", \"from\": 3853, \"to\": 3901, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When he looked inward, he noticed how exhaustedbeingNoah Lyles made Noah Lyles.\", \"from\": 3902, \"to\": 3981, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3970, \"end\": 3980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He committed to fewer events off the track, took fewer offers and searched for balance, not more sprints.\", \"from\": 3982, \"to\": 4087, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He worked to create boundaries, to worry less about pleasing those outside his circle.\", \"from\": 4088, \"to\": 4174, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And so that became his pattern\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094and he gotfaster.\", \"from\": 4176, \"to\": 4226, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He spoke about wanting to \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009ctranscend\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d track and field, as Allyson Felix had.\", \"from\": 4227, \"to\": 4307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4289, \"end\": 4302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allyson_Felix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Allyson Felix\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allyson_Felix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allyson_Felix\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As his mouth motored, Lyles turned his attention to achieving The Double in Paris.\", \"from\": 4308, \"to\": 4390, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4330, \"end\": 4335, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.7652086834710999, \"rank\": 0.30682580981056595, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 4384, \"end\": 4389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.884761056043172e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyles went to Budapest in August 2023 for the world championships.\", \"from\": 4392, \"to\": 4458, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4406, \"end\": 4414, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2793752600222942e-13, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/re