Peter_Pan\", \"score\": 0.999999999992724, \"rank\": 7.0017241924497985e-12, \"text\": \"Peter Pan\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Pan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Pan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, she says, he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s still dressing up.\", \"from\": 6840, \"to\": 6880, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cHe\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s always been really creative and quirky and just \\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 him,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d says Keisha.\", \"from\": 6882, \"to\": 6964, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6957, \"end\": 6963, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keisha_Buchanan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keisha\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keisha_Buchanan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keisha_Buchanan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cHe polishes his nails and wears his hair in different colors and loves fashion.\", \"from\": 6965, \"to\": 7047, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I really believe he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s an artist who runs fast.\", \"from\": 7048, \"to\": 7096, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s how I look at it.\", \"from\": 7097, \"to\": 7123, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And artists are just weird.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Can Lyles\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094the weird artist\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094become track\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s first superstar since Usain Bolt?\", \"from\": 7124, \"to\": 7237, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7226, \"end\": 7236, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Usain Bolt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Michael Johnson, the only man to win both the 200 and 400 meters at the same Olympics (Atlanta in 1996), is planning to start a new international track league, Grand Slam Track.\", \"from\": 7239, \"to\": 7416, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7239, \"end\": 7254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\", \"score\": 0.6562406956371172, \"rank\": 0.27532889874358996, \"text\": \"Michael Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\"}, {\"begin\": 7326, \"end\": 7333, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1070020053592614e-19, \"text\": \"Atlanta\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The success of the league depends on closing the gap between how Americans view the sport and how much of the rest of the world views it.\", \"from\": 7417, \"to\": 7554, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He needs personalities who shine in major competitions.\", \"from\": 7555, \"to\": 7610, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Says Johnson, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWe\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re seeing the greatest collection of stand-out personalities in this sport since I was competing.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Lyles, and such charismatic athletes as Sha\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099Carri Richardson and Kenny Bednarek, Johnson says,inspiredthe league he is creating.\", \"from\": 7611, \"to\": 7865, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7616, \"end\": 7623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"score\": 0.982811074744544, \"rank\": 0.017489530555302873, \"text\": \"Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\"}, {\"begin\": 7735, \"end\": 7740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"s